# handless

> This repository is currently under construction. Its API might change at any time without notice nor major version bump.

A Python dependency injection container that automatically resolves and injects dependencies without polluting your code with framework-specific decorators. Inspired by Lagom, Svcs, and C# .NET DI, it keeps your code clean and flexible while offering multiple service registration options. ðŸš€

## Contributing

Running tests: `uv run pytest tests --cov=containers --cov-report=term-missing`
